{"tid":2370318,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：祭品食家李薇 濫用長者八達通斷正（李八方）","createTime":"2021-01-18T02:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T06:52:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"19c14c0ca1990e659f78e8ce25a66db21ffcfbea","tid":2370318,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T02:59:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210118/YCJVGITBAVDJ5AAGR7G7PMN3JU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210118%2FYCJVGITBAVDJ5AAGR7G7PMN3JU%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS0qdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=2e706b22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210118%2FYCJVGITBAVDJ5AAGR7G7PMN3JU%2F&h=222953e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210118/YCJVGITBAVDJ5AAGR7G7PMN3JU/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：祭品食家李薇 濫用長者八達通斷正（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/d-Mifw1PB1goWPtnf8mN7OsAm8A=/1892x1208/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EDJZOEZNZVH4JI7LQXZTCW5B44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fd-Mifw1PB1goWPtnf8mN7OsAm8A%3D%2F1892x1208%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEDJZOEZNZVH4JI7LQXZTCW5B44.jpg&h=036fa28b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家記唔記得中大有個好「識食」嘅女教授李薇？呢位中大政治及行政學系助理教授，上年唔滿意市民浪費食物，竟將農曆七月市民路祭嘅食品執返去煮成三餸一湯，全城譁然，但佢就擺出一副「我開心關你屁事」態度，換嚟祭品食家外號。最近佢又成為網上紅人，今次唔關祭品事，而係有人疑濫用長者八達通斷正，喺港鐵站發爛渣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ahw2bw0P1svkWfG4ZWYpX50bG9k=/2102x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HF5BXKRZD5F25F2VVOHBJQBB5I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fahw2bw0P1svkWfG4ZWYpX50bG9k%3D%2F2102x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHF5BXKRZD5F25F2VVOHBJQBB5I.jpg&h=96d7e6d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■李薇喺深水埗站用長者八達通斷正，喺大堂失控尖叫，港鐵五職員將佢圍住。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DHs_UUXm1eugxWiCYVXPPwXrf6k=/583x434/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YDBGIGSJLVA4HGW5I4UQ3MAW7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDHs_UUXm1eugxWiCYVXPPwXrf6k%3D%2F583x434%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYDBGIGSJLVA4HGW5I4UQ3MAW7U.jpg&h=c7ec4470&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李薇祭品餐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發爛渣屈馬嶽違反國安<br />\n<br />\n網傳片段李薇喺深水埗站俾職員捉到正用長者八達通，喺大堂失控尖叫，要黨鐵出動五個男女職員手拉手將佢圍住，李教授全力頑抗黨鐵霸權，解釋「用錯咗八達通」冇用，就斥黨鐵職員係「資本家嘅走狗」，後來職員搵PoPo求救，但李教授見PoPo竟然改玩「篤灰」，訓斥佢哋「點解唔搵我同事馬嶽（中大政政系副教授），你哋點解唔搵我同事李家翹（中大政政系講師），佢違反國安法！我用錯八達通你哋就拉！」<br />\n<br />\nPoPo話前日接獲港鐵職員報案，話一名女子喺深水埗港鐵站疑使用特惠八達通卡入閘，職員向該女子查票但對方不合作，於是報警，案件列作「違反《香港鐵路附例》」交港鐵處理，而中大就話如有大學成員被裁定觸犯法例，校方會按既定程序處理。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"cc5b6ebf05b330b1fe0ef522dcf074b5f9a78c65","tid":2370318,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T06:52:30.000Z","msg":"有冇聯署叫中大炒佢？"}]}